TEMPLATE RECURSION
An N-Dimensional Grid: First Attempt

//--------------------------------------------
How singleDGrid[3] = 5; works

Step 1: 
        singleDGrid[3]
        Calls OneDGrid<int>::operator
        Returns a reference to the int stored at index 3.

Step 2: 
        = 5;
        Assigns the value 5 into that reference.
        So internally:
        mElements[3] = 5;
